data.description:
Welcome to 11406 Caleigh Anne Dr, a stunning 4-bedroom, 3-bathroom residence on over half an acre (in a cul de sac!) with fruit producing trees. This home combines spacious living with luxurious amenities, making it a haven of comfort and style.

As you step inside, the high, beamed ceiling draws you in as the well-designed floor plan unfolds, revealing a chef's kitchen that is both functional and elegant. The kitchen seamlessly flows into a spacious living area, creating a central hub for daily life. Just outside the back door you'll find a large covered patio with a fireplace and an outdoor kitchen complete with sink and fridge.

To the left you'll find the 3 secondary rooms and 2 full baths - one with a stand up shower and a door leading to the covered back patio. 

To the right you'll find a spacious primary bedroom and the laundry room (with a sink, cabinets and shoe storage attached to the wall). 

Upstairs, a generously sized game room awaits, offering endless possibilities for entertainment and leisure. Ample storage throughout ensures that every inch of space is as practical as it is beautiful.

Situated on a large, private cul-de-sac lot enveloped with fruit producing trees, this home guarantees a tranquil environment, ideal for those seeking a peaceful escape.  

With highly rated schools, Belton Lake, Baylor Scott & White, Killeen, and Waco in close proximity, this property is a dream for outdoor enthusiasts, offering a prime location for recreation, leisure, employment and quality educational opportunities.
